COSTA MESA MOTORCYCLE CRASH KILLS MAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A man was killed Tuesday when his motorcycle crashed near the intersection of 
Anton Boulevard and Sunflower Avenue, police said. 
</P>
<P>
 The man, who has not been identified, died after his motorcycle ran off Anton 
Boulevard at 8:50 p.m., according to Lt. Gary Webster.  
</P>
<P>
 No other vehicles were involved, and the cause of the accident is still under 
investigation. 
</P>
