 Buena (21-3-5) went up in the shootout, 1-0, on a goal from Monica Almaraz. 
Esperanza tied it on a goal by Jenny Parkison. Megan Munday and Barbara Almaraz 
scored for Buena and Tammy Lyon and Diana Guy kept it even for Esperanza. 
</P>
<P>
 The key save came when Esperanza goalie Chris Gehrls knocked away a shot by 
Allyson Munday. That gave Gallo the chance to win it. 
