</P>
<P>
 Craig Martin had 24 points and Darren Lax had 22 for Concordia, which ended 
the season 17-14.Lax had 19 points in the first half as the Eagles opened a 
43-32 lead. Robert Amo Amo scored 17 points, 14 in the second half. Point Loma 
is 15-16. 
</P>
<P>
 In another Golden State Athletic Conference playoff game: 
</P>
