<P>
 Basketball / Forward 
</P>
<P>
 Basketball is something Johnson does, albeit very well, while waiting for 
softball season. Johnson, a first baseman, already has signed to attend 
Oklahoma on a softball scholarship next fall.Meanwhile, she is passing the time 
as one of the better basketball players around. She helped Cypress to its first 
