<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE 36TH ANNUAL GRAMMY AWARDS; WHAT THEY SAID 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "I'd like to give a message to the young people of America: That is, we'll 
continue to abuse our position and (bleep) up the mainstream.' 
</P>
