</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Film director -- Jennifer Lynch is the sole director of "Welcome to the Edge," 
a new live-action special-effects advertising campaign for cable's Sci-Fi 
Channel. Wednesday's Morning Report implied that her father, David Lynch, is 
directing the project with her. 
</P>
